title.narrative: PNG Road Maintenance and Rehabilitation Project II

description.narrative: The project development objectives are to: (i) improve road transport to project areas through providing satisfactory physical condition and safety in selected roads; and (ii) strengthen institutional arrangements for road maintenance, including the participationof the private sector and communities; and (iii) enhance road-related economic opportunities for women.
